\n```\r\nNo, @[salary_sum][ per|per?] [@[paymentPeriod:hour]|@[paymentPeriod:day]|@[paymentPeriod:week]|@[paymentPeriod:month]|@[paymentPeriod:year]]\r\n```\r\nto generate\r\n```\r\n- No, [4500.00](salary_sum) per [annum](paymentPeriod:year)\r\n- No, [4500.00](salary_sum) per [d](paymentPeriod:day)\r\n- No, [4500.00](salary_sum) per [day](paymentPeriod:day)\r\n- No, [4500.00](salary_sum) per [h](paymentPeriod:hour)\r\n- No, [4500.00](salary_sum) per [hour](paymentPeriod:hour)\r\n```\r\n\r\nbut I want to make the template shorter\r\nlike\r\n```\r\nNo, @[salary_sum][ per|per?] @[paymentPeriod]\r\n```","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/SimGus/Chatette/issues/comments/559748338/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"alifanov","id":2394285,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIzOTQyODU=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2394285?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/alifanov","html_url":"https://github.com/alifanov","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/alifanov/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/alifanov/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/alifanov/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/alifanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/alifanov/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/alifanov/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/alifanov/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/alifanov/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/alifanov/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/SimGus/Chatette/issues/comments/559931703","html_url":"https://github.com/SimGus/Chatette/issues/30#issuecomment-559931703","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/SimGus/Chatette/issues/30","id":559931703,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDU1OTkzMTcwMw==","user":{"login":"SimGus","id":20604236,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIwNjA0MjM2","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/20604236?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/SimGus","html_url":"https://github.com/SimGus","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SimGus/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SimGus/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SimGus/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SimGus/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SimGus/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SimGus/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SimGus/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SimGus/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SimGus/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2019-11-30T09:08:12Z","updated_at":"2019-11-30T09:08:12Z","author_association":"OWNER","body":"I  see. Then, I suppose your solution is a good one. To make it easier to reuse your slots, I would suggest using a template such as this:\r\n```\r\n... your slot definitions ...\r\n~[paymentPeriod]\r\n   @[paymentPeriod:day]\r\n   @[paymentPeriod:hour]\r\n   ...\r\n```\r\n\r\nYou can then use this alias as if it was a slot, rather than needing to write the same list of slots over and over again ;)\r\n\r\nFor the record, it is also sometimes useful to use variations of slots (but I’m guessing this will not be a solution in your case), like this:\r\n```\r\n@[paymentPeriod#hour]\r\n   hour\r\n   h\r\n@[paymentPeriod#day]\r\n   day\r\n   d\r\n```\r\nYou can then use the slot `@[paymentPeriod]` as if it was defined, and the generator will choose one of the variations at random. However, in that case, the name of the generated entity will be `paymentPeriod` and not the name of the chosen variation.\r\n\r\nI understand that in your case, none of the solutions I suggested is totally satisfying. I’ll see if I can make some changes that would help in your situation, because I guess such cases must come up often.\r\n\r\nThanks for your questions :)","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/SimGus/Chatette/issues/comments/559931703/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"SimGus","id":20604236,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIwNjA0MjM2","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/20604236?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/SimGus","html_url":"https://github.com/SimGus","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SimGus/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SimGus/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SimGus/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SimGus/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SimGus/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SimGus/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SimGus/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SimGus/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/SimGus/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/SimGus/Chatette/issues/comments/563137686","html_url":"https://github.com/SimGus/Chatette/issues/30#issuecomment-563137686","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/SimGus/Chatette/issues/30","id":563137686,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDU2MzEzNzY4Ng==","user":{"login":"alifanov","id":2394285,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIzOTQyODU=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2394285?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/alifanov","html_url":"https://github.com/alifanov","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/alifanov/followers","following_url":"https://api.gi